It depends on the day you play, the level changes depending on the day.

depende del da en que juegues,el nivel cambia dependiendo del dia.

Version 1.1
Fix of "Fall-Away Freights," a late summer 2021 level. There were some broken cannons, now they're fixed and you can play the level with no crash. #8992-067F - 12/22/23 - 3:10pm
In Oct. 2021, I made a level called "Woody Purple Fiends," but due to a glitch, I changed the title by "Black Killer Holes." Now there's a game crash there, so I did some cleanup to fix everything.
A fortress filled with interesting contraptions Bowser threw in.

Solve difficult puzzles while keeping Mario on his toes in this icy but warm ghost house.   

To carry Flurries, check out the Flurry Carrying level. You'll solve the first puzzle much quicker.
